<div style="max-width: 720px; margin: 40px auto; font-family: system-ui;">
  <h1>Account & Data Deletion Request</h1>

  <p>
    You may request the deletion of your account and associated data at any time.
  </p>

  <h3>What data will be deleted</h3>
  <ul>
    <li>User profile and account information</li>
    <li>Messages between client and assigned coach</li>
    <li>App usage and related records</li>
  </ul>

  <p>
    Some information may be retained if required by law.
  </p>

  <h3>How to request deletion</h3>
  <p>
    Submit your registered email address below.
  </p>

  <%= form_with url: account_deletion_path, method: :post do %>
    <div style="margin-bottom: 12px;">
      <label>Email address</label><br>
      <%= email_field_tag :email, nil, required: true, style: "width:100%; padding:8px;" %>
    </div>

    <%= submit_tag "Request Account Deletion",
          style: "padding:10px 16px; background:#0e3264; color:#fff; border:none;" %>
  <% end %>

  <p style="margin-top: 24px;">
    Deletion requests are processed within <strong>30 days</strong>.
  </p>

  <p>
    For help, contact: <a href="mailto:contact@mycustomsleepjourney.com">contact@mycustomsleepjourney.com</a>
  </p>
</div>
